Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>With weakness as my ally</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>yowasa wo mikata ni tsuketa boku wa</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I soar higher than anybody else</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>dare yori mo takaku toberu no dakara</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>It's a pity to linger in a place like this</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>konna tokoro de tomatte tara</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>For the things that's been lost will lose their spark</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>nakushita mono ga kagayakanaku naru</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>At times when you're lost somewhere</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>kimi ga dokoka mayotta tokini</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>If my heart is also adrift</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>boku no kokoro mo samayotte itara</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I won't be able to find you</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>mitsukete agerarenainda</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Your kindness, nor your strength</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>yasashisa dake janaku sono tsuyosa mo</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I already know</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>wakatterunda</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>It's the break of dawn</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>yoake no toki sa</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>To the highest point of reach</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>saikou toutatsu ten ni made</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I'll dash through all the way, yeah</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>ikki ni kakenukete iku kara, yeah</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I bet you're laughing, numbed by it all</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>mahi shite waratterundarou</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>For the pain of those days is now in the past, perhaps</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>ano hibino itami mo kako dakara tabun</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>With the world as my enemy</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>sekai wo teki ni shinagara</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I stand my ground on quivering legs</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>kuzuresouna ashi de fumitodomaru</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Keep moving, just a bit more for me</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>ato sukoshi dake ugoite kure</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>The awakening moment\NThe time of resurrection has come, now</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>saa fukkatsu da mezame no toki ga kita ima</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>The awakening moment\NThe time of resurrection has come, now</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>saa fukkatsu da mezame no toki ga kita ima</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Finally, the curtain falls on\N20 years of revenge by the Kozuki Clan...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>...in the battle above the Land of Wano.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>The winner...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Straw Hat Luffy.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>"He Returns!\NThe Shogun of the Land of Wano, Kozuki Momonosuke"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No... You're all mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to run...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that dragon we saw was Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, there are two dragons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If that wasn't Kaido-sama,\Nwho was that dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Komurasaki-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on in front of the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all about, Boss Kyoshiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if everyone remembers us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,K-K-Kin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kin'emon-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Foxfire Kin'emon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! I thought he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the burning castle that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he here?!\NAm I dreaming just as I thought?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we in the other world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we die at some point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't care\Nif I'm dreaming or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like something big\Nis about to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokozuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamatsu-sama, the Kappa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogstorm-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Raizo of the Mist is here, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat Viper-dono and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikunojo-sama of the Fallen Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Kyoshiro, what is this all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Napping Kyoshiro is\Nan alternate identity to hide my origin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In actuality, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...a member of the Akazaya Nine,\NDenjiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt! They're the Akazaya Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Akazaya came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought all of them died 20 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What Toki-sama said was true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Set up a Light-Scroll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the whole country know! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,An image from the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, go to Bakura Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,RINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Something has happened at the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,HAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this about the earthquake earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,KIBI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that\Nthe whole region was gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Forget about the broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,EBISU TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're receiving a transmission\Nfrom the Flower Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll play the Light-Scroll!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... What?!\NThe battle isn't over yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! I'm not your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always read about you guys\Nin newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had my doubts\Nas to whether many of you were humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say Kaido's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san! I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm gonna join your crew\Nfrom now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamato A.K.A. Kozuki Oden!\NIt's good to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna join us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What a funny boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't accept that\Nuntil we hear it from our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Luffy will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But that battle gave me chills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he fought!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like, whack, bam, ka-boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was awesome!\NI wish you were there to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we shouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll do to us what we did to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said you could leave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't wanna be slaves,\NYoung Master Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, or I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,An escape?!\NThat's unbecoming of a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and stay there, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'll punish you!\N--Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like he's not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, what will happen to those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My power will be undone\Nwhen the same moon rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, in a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Some animals will turn back to normal\Nafter a month...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...but some will stay tamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--I see.\N--Maybe it depends on their character?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they'll choose\Nwhichever is more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Neigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Master-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happier staying as I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Horselina-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish for you to stay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But not as a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to stay with me forever\Nlike a mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Horselina-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Master-sama... Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Horselina-chan!\NYou're holding me a little too tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama and Horselina...\NI'm happy for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Komurasaki, Kin-san, and the others\Nknelt down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...twenty years\Nsince my father Kozuki Oden died!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Father"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad that you lived through...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...the long, hard years!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...twenty years\Nsince my father Kozuki Oden died!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Father"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad that you lived through...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...the long, hard years!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--I'm confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fire Festival will not end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow,\Nyou can start whatever business you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! But Orochi will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drink all you want, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well water will be free of charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The factories will not be allowed\Nto release poison that ruins the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Land of Wano is no place for slavery!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo... <i>kun</i>?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not need to suffer anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Four more died at the factory today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that will be me tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to tell Otama-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Otama-chan, I hate to tell you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...your father and mother are already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Woven hats for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody need a hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're tough and durable!\NIt's a great deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want a hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hats for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody need a hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Komachiyo, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sell any hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody need a hat?!\NHats for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A hat! Does anybody need a hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tengu-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an orphan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a few years more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When the strong samurai group\Nnamed Kozuki returns,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll signal the downfall of the demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozuki will take down the demons for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stay strong!\NI'm going to be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Otama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Master-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Tama!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I'll make it your everyday life!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time we leave this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it a place where\Nyou can eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi's tyranny...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the days of\Nbeing threatened by Kaido are over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The dependable friends I made\Nacross the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Ninja-Pirate-Mink-Samurai Alliance,\Nwe raided Onigashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido, Orochi,\Nand the Animal Kingdom Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All the evils\Nthat threatened this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have punished them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you take down those monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That hateful Orochi is gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to be afraid anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can drink clean water!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The hellish days are over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally... Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We will never forget those\Nwho helped us accomplish the raid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What else should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just show off a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Are you just a figurehead, Momo?!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything left in the world\Nthat can scare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The name my father gave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...means "peerless"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lead this country,\Neven the ruined land will turn into Xanadu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to work\Nand help me make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending 20 years of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here to save you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Kozuki Momonosuke,\Nwill rule the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Mother!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I will keep my promise to you!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Father!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>I will follow in your footsteps!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Shogun family came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We were waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>In the skies of the future,\Nas a warrior sheathes his sword,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>flower petals flutter.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>This is the famous samurai country.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>The 8-year-old handsome man\Ngazes up to the cherry blossoms at night.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>He is more loyal and empathic\Nthan anyone else.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>He is not a man of great strength.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>The great Shogun of the Land of Wano,\NKozuki Momonosuke,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>who will earn his place in history,\Nnow rises!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>"Time's up"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>"jikan gire sa"</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Someone laughed again</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>dareka ga mata waratta</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>All right, now hide-and-seek</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>joutou saa kakurenbo wa</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Is over</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>owari</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Let's go, come on\N(We can see it soon)</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>ikou hora\N(mou sugu mieru)</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Make our hearts beat loudly\N(Our island)</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>kodoku nari kishimase\N(boku tachi no shima ga)</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Something will change\N(We can see it soon)</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>nanika ga kawaru\N(mou sugu mieru)</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Be tough, there's still time\N(1-2-3)</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>chikara zuyoku nare jikan wa aru zo\N(1-2-3)</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Let's raise it</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>kakage you</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We can't go on\NLiving a life of nothing but loneliness</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>kono mune afureteru\Nkodoku dake ja ikirenai</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We're young, so we're free</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>osanai boku ra nara jiyuu dana</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>A foolish dream</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>baka na yume</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We live it</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>ikiru</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>We'll illuminate the dark path ahead</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>mienai saki wo terashite yuku</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Get on our feet and try</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>jibun no ashi de Try</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Let's see the ends of the world together</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>sekai no hate wo tomo ni miyou</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>Together we can go and fly</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,<i>issho nara ikeru Fly</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We will tell you all about the bravery\Nof Luffy-senpai in the battle against Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Be ready to carve his freewheeling rampage\Ninto your memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Luffy is having a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Luffy-senpai Support Project! Barto's Secret Room 4!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai's gonna become the King of the Pirates!